room_title: Escape room "Ice Storm" by Escape Hatch - Bixby in Tulsa
review: We had a great first time experience at Bixby Escape Hatch! Family friendly, personable staff, and so much fun! Loved doing the Ice Storm room in the dark...added a whole other level to the challenge! Highly recommend!!

room_title: Escape room "Ice Storm" by Escape Hatch - Bixby in Tulsa
review: My first time in an escape room. It was awesome! We were in the Ice Storm room, made it out with 6 minutes to spare! Can't wait to try the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Ice Storm" by Escape Hatch - Bixby in Tulsa
review: Our family of six had a great time with the Ice Storm challenge. Very creative and fun.
